==Awards and nominations==
{{Main|List of awards and nominations received by One Direction}}

One Direction have been recipients of two [[BRIT Award]]s<U+2014>winning their first with "What Makes You Beautiful" for Best British Single at the [[2012 BRIT Awards]],<ref name=BestBritishSingle>{{cite news |url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/one-direction/news/brit-awards-2012-british-single/ |title=One Direction Win Best British Single At BRIT Awards 2012 |work=[[Capital (radio network)|Capital FM]]|publisher=[[Global Radio]] |date=21 February 2011 |accessdate=15 March 2012}}</ref> three [[NME awards]],<ref>{{cite news|title=Arctic Monkeys, Noel Gallagher, The Vaccines, Lana Del Rey nominated for NME Awards 2012|url=http://www.nme.com/news/arctic-monkeys/61733|work=NME|publisher=[[IPC Media]]|accessdate=15 February 2012|date=30 January 2012}}</ref> two [[Kids' Choice Awards]],<ref>{{cite web|last=Hewett |first=Emily |url=http://www.metro.co.uk/music/894873-one-direction-steal-the-show-at-nickelodeon-kids-choice-awards |title=One Direction steal the show at Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards|work=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro]]|publisher=[[Associated Newspapers]] |date=20 April 2012 |accessdate= 27 April 2012}}</ref> and four [[MTV Video Music Awards]],<ref name=videomusicawards/> [[List of awards and nominations received by One Direction|among other awards]]. One Direction won all nine awards they were nominated for at the 2012 [[Teen Choice Awards]].<ref>{{cite news| first = Tina | last = Hart |url=http://www.musicweek.com/news/read/swift-and-bieber-big-winners-at-teen-choice-awards/051089 | title =Swift and Bieber big winners at Teen Choice Awards |work=[[Music Week]] |publisher=Intent Media |date= 23 July 2012 |accessdate=27 July 2012}}</ref> One Direction also won two [[American Music Awards]] out of their two nominations for [[American Music Award for Favorite Pop/Rock Album|Favorite Pop/Rock Album]] and [[American Music Award for Favorite Pop/Rock Band/Duo/Group|Favorite Pop/Rock Band/Duo/Group]], respectively.

